<view class="page">
  <view class="tips" wx:if="{{useFallback}}">
    {{usingMockData ? '当前展示开发环境演示数据（含状态历史），连接后端后可查看实时数据。' : '当前展示本地缓存通知数据，连接后端后可查看实时数据。'}}
  </view>

  <view class="center-switch">
    <view
      wx:for="{{centerTabs}}"
      wx:key="value"
      class="center-switch-item {{activeCenterTab === item.value ? 'active' : ''}}"
      bindtap="onCenterTabTap"
      data-value="{{item.value}}"
    >
      {{item.label}}
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="school-sub-entry" bindtap="onOpenSchoolSubscription">
    <view class="school-sub-entry-main">
      <text class="school-sub-entry-title">学校级通知设置</text>
      <text class="school-sub-entry-desc">按学校统一设置通知开关，新增公告自动继承</text>
    </view>
    <text class="school-sub-entry-arrow">→</text>
  </view>

  <view class="section-title">我关注的公告</view>
  <view class="empty" wx:if="{{progressList.length === 0}}">
    <text>还没有关注公告，先去夏令营/预推免详情页点击“已关注”。</text>
    <button class="primary-btn" bindtap="onOpenCampList">去看公告</button>
  </view>

  <view class="progress-list" wx:else>
    <view
      class="progress-item"
      wx:for="{{progressList}}"
      wx:key="id"
      data-id="{{item.id}}"
      bindtap="onOpenProgressDetail"
    >
      <view class="row">
        <text class="title">{{item.campTitle}}</text>
        <text class="status">{{item.stageText}}</text>
      </view>
      <view class="meta-row">
        <text>{{item.universityName}}</text>
        <text>截止: {{item.deadlineText}}</text>
      </view>
      <text class="next-action">建议：{{item.nextAction}}</text>
      <view class="meta-row">
        <text>更新于 {{item.updatedAtText}}</text>
        <text>{{item.subscriptionEnabled ? '通知已开启' : '通知未开启'}}</text>
      </view>
    </view>
  </view>
</view>
